[gd_scene load_steps=17 format=3 uid="uid://bcuttle007"]

; Clean-room cuttlefish-like aerial enemy. Elongated capsule body (authored
; along +Z) with top-mounted eyes, top fin-crest, long side fins, rear siphon
; funnel, chromatophore spots, and six tentacles hanging down-and-outward.
; Origin sits at body center (no feet — it's aerial). enemy.gd rotates 180°
; on instantiate so the body ends up facing -Z in world. AnimationPlayer
; autoplays "drift" so the creature undulates/sways even when static.

